 Anthropic 推出新的 Claude AI 模型和“计算机控制” https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/anthropic-new-claude-ai-models-and-computer-control/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=anthropic-new-claude-ai-models-and-computer -控制https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/anthropic-new-claude-ai-models-and-computer-control/#respondRyan Daws Tue, 22 Oct 2024 16:07:38 +0000 ApplicationsArtificial IntelligenceChatbotsCompaniesDevelopmentaianthropicartificial intelligenceclaudehaikullmmodelssonnet https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/?p=16365 <p> Anthropic 宣布升级其人工智能产品组合，包括增强的 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 模型和引入 Claude 3.5 Haiku，以及公开测试版中的“计算机控制”功能。升级后的 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 在所有指标上都显示出显着的改进，尤其是在编码能力方面的进步尤其显着。该模型在<a class="excerpt-read-more" href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/anthropic-new-claude-ai-models-and-computer-control/" title="ReadAnthropic 推出新的克劳德人工智能模型和“计算机控制”">... 上取得了令人印象深刻的 49.0% 阅读更多 ”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/anthropic-new-claude-ai-models-and-computer-control/">Anthropic 发布了新的 Claude AI 模型，“计算机控制”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com">AI News</a>上。</p> ; 
<p><a href="https://www.anthropic.com/">Anthropic</a>宣布升级其人工智能产品组合，包括增强的 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 模型和引入 Claude 3.5 Haiku，以及公开测试版中的“计算机控制”功能。</p><p>升级后的 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 在所有指标上都显示出显着的改进，尤其是在编码能力方面的进步尤其显着。该模型在 SWE-bench Verified 基准测试中取得了令人印象深刻的 49.0%，超过了所有公开可用的模型，包括 OpenAI 的产品和专业编码系统。</p><p>在一项开创性的开发中，Anthropic 引入了计算机使用功能，使 Claude 能够像人类一样与计算机进行交互：查看屏幕、控制光标、单击和打字。该功能目前处于公开测试阶段，标志着 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 成为第一个提供此类功能的前沿人工智能模型。 </p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe title="克劳德|使用计算机实现自动化操作" width="1200" height="675" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ODaHJzOyVCQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></figure><p>几家主要科技公司已经开始实施这些新功能。</p><p> GitLab 报告称：“升级后的 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 代表了人工智能编码的重大飞跃。”该报告指出，跨用例的推理能力增强了 10%，且没有额外的延迟。</p><p>新的 Claude 3.5 Haiku 型号将于本月晚些时候发布，其性能与之前的 Claude 3 Opus 相匹配，同时保持成本效益和速度。它在 SWE-bench Verified 上取得了 40.6% 的成绩，优于许多竞争模型，包括原始的 Claude 3.5 Sonnet 和 GPT-4o。 </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1024" height="761" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-1024x761.jpg" alt="模型基准比较 Anthropic 的新 Claude AI 模型。" class="wp-image-16366" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-1024x761.jpg 1024w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-300x223.jpg 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-768x570.jpg 768w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-1536x1141.jpg 1536w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-2048x1521.jpg 2048w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-269x200.jpg 269w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-380x282.jpg 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-337x250.jpg 337w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-100x74.jpg 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/anthropic-new-claude-3.5-ai-models-benchmark-compare-computer-control-artificial-intelligence-sonnet-haiku-60x45.jpg 60w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> <em>（来源：人类）</em></figcaption></figure><p>关于计算机控制能力，Anthropic 采取了谨慎的方法，承认当前的局限性，同时强调潜力。在评估计算机界面导航的 OSWorld 基准测试中，Claude 3.5 Sonnet 在仅屏幕截图测试中取得了 14.9% 的成绩，明显优于次优系统的 7.8%。</p><p>这些开发项目经过了严格的<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/uk-and-us-sign-pact-develop-ai-safety-tests/">安全评估</a>，并与美国和英国人工智能安全研究所合作进行了部署前测试。 Anthropic 认为 ASL-2 标准（如其负责任的扩展政策中详述）仍然适合这些模型。</p><p> （图片来源：人类）</p><p><strong>另请参阅：</strong> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/ibm-granite-3-ai-models-open-source-commitment/"><strong>IBM 推出承诺开源的 Granite 3.0 AI 模型</strong></a></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/"><img decoding="async" width="728" height="90" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png" alt="" class="wp-image-11874" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png 728w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-300x37.png 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-380x47.png 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-350x43.png 350w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-100x12.png 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-60x7.png 60w" sizes="(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px" /></a></figure><p><strong>想向行业领导者了解更多关于人工智能和大数据的知识吗？</strong>查看在阿姆斯特丹、加利福尼亚州和伦敦举办的<a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/">人工智能与大数据博览会</a>。该综合活动与<a href="https://intelligentautomation-conference.com/northamerica/">智能自动化大会</a>、 <a href="https://www.blockchain-expo.com/">BlockX</a> 、<a href="https://digitaltransformation-week.com/">数字化转型周</a>以及<a href="https://www.cybersecuritycloudexpo.com/">网络安全与云博览会</a>等其他领先活动同期举行。</p><p><a href="https://techforge.pub/events/">在此</a>探索由 TechForge 提供支持的其他即将举行的企业技术活动和网络研讨会。</p><p> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/anthropic-new-claude-ai-models-and-computer-control/">Anthropic 发布了新的 Claude AI 模型，“计算机控制”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com">AI News</a>上。</p> ; https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/anthropic-new-claude-ai-models